OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,FReporting by ITV News Social Affairs
OL,7,FCorrespondent Sarah Corker and ITV
OL,8,FNews Social Affairs Producer Lottie
OL,9,FKilraine
OL,11,FWARNING: This article contains
OL,12,Fdistressing content.
OL,14,F"It was a death by neglect and
OL,15,Fcruelty. There wasn't a teaspoon of
OL,16,Flove in that place."
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@TO]
