OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,FAnnette McKay is searching for her
OL,7,Flost sister. Mary Margaret was born in
OL,8,Fthe now notorious Catholic-run mother
OL,9,Fand baby home in Tuam, County Galway,
OL,10,FIreland, in the 1940s.
OL,12,FShe died aged just six months old from
OL,13,Fwhooping cough and heart failure -
OL,14,Fthen all trace of her vanished.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784751301
OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,FThe Galway town is now at the centre
OL,7,Fof a sinister discovery that has
OL,8,Fshocked the world; for decades the
OL,9,Fremains of hundreds of dead babies and
OL,10,Fchildren from St. Mary's home for
OL,11,Funmarried mothers were put in a
OL,12,Fdisused septic tank.
OL,14,FA mass grave for 796 infants, denied
OL,15,Feven the most basic level of dignity
OL,16,Fin life and death.
OL,18,FAnnette, who lives in Bury in Greater
OL,19,FManchester, believes her sister is
OL,20,Famong the 796.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784751301
OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,F"They were just ghost children. There
OL,7,Fare no photos, no evidence of what
OL,8,Fthey looked like, or who comforted
OL,9,Fthem. Nothing," Annette said.
OL,11,F"They were treated like trash. All I
OL,12,Fhave of my sister is a death
OL,13,Fcertificate."
OL,15,F"Tell us why that poor little girl and
OL,16,Flots of little girls had to suffer
OL,17,Flike that. We had to go begging and
OL,18,Fpleading for answers. I just want to
OL,19,Fknow the truth," she told ITV News.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@MO]wD@AOU{D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784751301
OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,FAfter years of campaigning, Annette
OL,7,Fsaid she will not give up until
OL,8,F"somebody is held accountable."
OL,10,FAnnette's mother, Maggie O'Connor, was
OL,11,Fsent to Tuam in 1943 as a pregnant 17-
OL,12,Fyear-old after she was raped.
OL,14,FShe was separated from her baby
OL,15,Fshortly after birth and forced to
OL,16,Fcarry out unpaid labour.
OL,18,FSix months later, she was told by a
OL,19,Fnun that "your child of sin is dead"
OL,20,Fand denied a funeral or proper burial
OL,21,Ffor her baby.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784751301
OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,FThe horrors of Tuam never left her,
OL,7,Fand she died in 2016 never knowing
OL,8,Fwhat happened to her daughter.
OL,10,FThe Tuam institution was run by an
OL,11,Forder of nuns, the Bon Secours
OL,12,FSisters, and owned by Galway County
OL,13,FCouncil, from 1925 until 1961.
OL,15,FDeath records suggest on average two
OL,16,Fbabies a week were dying there, many
OL,17,Fdue to malnutrition and treatable
OL,18,Fillnesses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784751301
OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,FThe institution was part of a network
OL,7,Fof so-called homes across Ireland
OL,8,Fwhere pregnant, unmarried women were
OL,9,Fsent to give birth in secret for much
OL,10,Fof the 20th century, and then forcibly
OL,11,Fseparated from their children.
OL,13,FA forensic excavation of Tuam's mass
OL,14,Fgrave is underway to try to identify
OL,15,Fhow and why so many children died
OL,16,Fthere.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784751301
OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,FThe team of investigators is being led
OL,7,Fby Daniel MacSweeney, a forensics
OL,8,Fexpert who previously worked for the
OL,9,FInternational Committee of the Red
OL,10,FCross in Iraq, Afghanistan and Yemen.
OL,12,FHe said the goal is to give a
OL,13,Frespectful burial to all the remains.
OL,15,FSpeaking on Wednesday, experts
OL,16,Finvolved in the excavation said the
OL,17,Fremains of 99 infants have now been
OL,18,Fdiscovered in a concentrated area,
OL,19,Fdescribing it as a "hugely significant
OL,20,Fdevelopment".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784751301
OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,FThey were found in coffins on a
OL,7,Fsection of the land where excavations
OL,8,Fare continuing.
OL,10,FAll of the bones recovered will be
OL,11,Ftaken to a new forensic laboratory at
OL,12,FToghermore, in Tuam, where the
OL,13,Fidentification process will begin.
OL,15,FThere has been a public appeal to
OL,16,Fanyone who suspects a family member
OL,17,Fmay have died in the Tuam institution
OL,18,Fto come forward to provide DNA to help
OL,19,Fidentify the children and match them
OL,20,Fwith any living relatives.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784751301
OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,FSo far 62 families have come forward.
OL,8,FIt was only due to the painstaking
OL,9,Fwork of a local historian, Catherine
OL,10,FCorless, that the truth came to light.
OL,12,FIn 2014 she uncovered the death
OL,13,Fcertificates of 796 children from the
OL,14,FTuam institution, but there were no
OL,15,Fburial records or graves. They ranged
OL,16,Ffrom newborns to four-year-olds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784751301
OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,F"I couldn't believe it, at the time
OL,7,Fthe authorities were trying to prevent
OL,8,Fme from putting out the information,
OL,9,Fthey didn't believe it," Catherine
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"But the number, 796 babies missing
OL,13,Fwas enough to give me the energy to
OL,14,Fkeep in fighting, and not give up."
OL,16,FCatherine's research indicated that
OL,17,Fthe children were buried on the site
OL,18,Fof the home in an underground disused
OL,19,Fsewage tank.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784751301
OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,FThe government and church tried to
OL,7,Fdismiss her work, but eventually,
OL,8,Fpreliminary tests found significant
OL,9,Fquantities of human remains at the
OL,10,Fsite.
OL,12,FThe findings sent shockwaves across
OL,13,FIreland, but it took another decade
OL,14,Ffor plans for the site's excavation to
OL,15,Fbe finalised, despite years of
OL,16,Fcampaigning by survivors and their
OL,17,Ffamilies.
OL,19,FThe exhumation process finally began
OL,20,Fin August 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784751301
OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,F"That's what I set out to do, to get
OL,7,Fthe babies out of a sewage system, for
OL,8,Fpeople to realise how horrific it was
OL,9,Fto do that to illegitimate children,
OL,10,Fand I still believe it's because they
OL,11,Fwere illegitimate" Catherine said.
OL,13,FShe believes the children died of
OL,14,Fneglect and that the nuns didn't think
OL,15,Fthey were worth saving.
OL,17,FThe excavation process is on a scale
OL,18,Fand level of complexity not seen
OL,19,Fbefore.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784751301
OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,FA world-leading team at Durham
OL,7,FUniversity, specialising in the
OL,8,Frecovery of infant remains, is
OL,9,Ftraining and advising those excavating
OL,10,Fthe Tuam site.
OL,12,FProfessor Becky Gowland explained how
OL,13,Fthe investigation had to be meticulous
OL,14,Fin its approach.
OL,16,F"When you're excavating a site, you're
OL,17,Fessentially destroying the site as you
OL,18,Fgo along, so you only get one chance
OL,19,Fto do it right," she said.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784751301
OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,F"We're doing everything we can to
OL,7,Fbring justice to the babies and the
OL,8,Ffamilies involved."
OL,10,FAnalysis of the remains may also be
OL,11,Fable to explain how the children died,
OL,12,Fand what the conditions were like in
OL,13,Fthe home at the time.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784751301
OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,F"There's going to be anthropological
OL,7,Fanalysis to create a profile of each
OL,8,Fperson. So how old they were when they
OL,9,Fdied, whether they were a boy or a
OL,10,Fgirl. Is there any evidence of
OL,11,Fmalnutrition, any evidence of neglect
OL,12,For abuse? We know that mortality was
OL,13,Fquite high in these homes," she
OL,14,Fcontinued.
OL,16,F"This form of evidence allows the
OL,17,Fchildren, in a way, to tell their
OL,18,Fstories. They were so disempowered and
OL,19,Fmarginalised within these homes, and
OL,20,Fis a way their bodies can, can provide
OL,21,Fa form of testimony."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30517
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784751301
OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,FAnnette says she won't rest until her
OL,7,Fsister is buried alongside her mother
OL,8,Fclose to their home in Greater
OL,9,FManchester.
OL,11,F"They should have been treated with
OL,12,Fdecency and respect. So I want Mary
OL,13,FMargaret returned to my mother. I
OL,14,Fdon't think that's too much to ask,"
OL,15,Fshe said.
OL,17,FShe added that her fight for justice
OL,18,Fis still only getting started.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30518
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784751301
OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,F"I always believe Ireland is not ready
OL,7,Fto listen. They're not ready to listen
OL,8,Fto what they did to their children.
OL,9,FThey're not ready to listen to what
OL,10,Fthey did to the women," Annette
OL,11,Fcontinued.
OL,13,FThe Bon Secour Sisters who ran the
OL,14,FTuam institution have previously
OL,15,Fadmitted that it had played a role in
OL,16,Fa "sorrowful" chapter of Irish history
OL,17,Fand said: "We did not live up to our
OL,18,FChristianity."
OL,20,FIt has contributed #2.14 million to
OL,21,Fthe cost of the excavation.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/21
