OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,FGalway County Council also apologised
OL,7,Fin 2021 for "failing mothers and
OL,8,Fchildren".
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FIn 2021, Taoiseach Micheal Martin
OL,16,Fformally apologised on behalf of the
OL,17,FIrish State to survivors of Mother and
OL,18,FBaby Homes across Ireland.
OL,26,@wD@Yrp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/21
