OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784751301
OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,FThe historic apology followed a
OL,7,Fgovernment-commissioned report
OL,8,Fdetailing a brutally oppressive
OL,9,Fculture and an infant mortality rate
OL,10,Fof approximately 15% across these
OL,11,Finstitutions.
OL,13,FAlthough there has been an inquiry, a
OL,14,Fcriminal investigation has never been
OL,15,Fopened.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/21
