OL,3,CExcavation work ongoing at the mass
OL,4,Cgrave of nearly 800 babies in Ireland
OL,6,FThe building of the former home was
OL,7,Fdemolished after it closed, and the
OL,8,Fsite is now situated in the middle of
OL,9,Fa housing estate. The excavation is
OL,10,Fexpected to continue well into 2027,
OL,11,Fwith analysis work likely to carry on
OL,12,Ffor several years after that.
